issue.body:
Hello, I came across this exception today. 

System.NotSupportedException: The property 'Join.PrimaryGroup' does not have a value set and no value generator is available for properties of type 'bool'. Either set a value for the property before adding the entity or configure a value generator for properties of type 'bool' in 'OnModelCreating'.

### Technical details

- EF Core Power Tools version: 2.6.72

- Exact Visual Studio version: Microsoft Visual Studio Professional 2022 (64-bit) - 17.8.5

- Database engine: SQL Server 2019

- EF Core version in use: 
Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.SqlServer 8.0.1
Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.SqlServer.NetTopologySuite 8.0.1

### Steps to reproduce a bug

**Create two tables:**
```
CREATE SCHEMA Testing;
GO

CREATE TABLE [Testing].[List](
	[Id] [uniqueidentifier] NOT NULL,
	[Description] [nvarchar](max) NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_TestingList] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[Id] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON, OPTIMIZE_FOR_SEQUENTIAL_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY] TEXTIMAGE_ON [PRIMARY]
GO

ALTER TABLE [Testing].[List] ADD  DEFAULT (newsequentialid()) FOR [Id]
GO

ALTER TABLE [Testing].[List]  WITH CHECK ADD  CONSTRAINT [CK_ID] CHECK  (([Id]<>'00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'))
GO

ALTER TABLE [Testing].[List] CHECK CONSTRAINT [CK_ID]
GO


CREATE TABLE [Testing].[Joins](
	[TargetId] [uniqueidentifier] NOT NULL,
	[SourceId] [uniqueidentifier] NOT NULL,
	[PrimaryGroup] [bit] NOT NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_Way] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[TargetId] ASC,
	[SourceId] ASC,
	[PrimaryGroup] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON, OPTIMIZE_FOR_SEQUENTIAL_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]
GO

ALTER TABLE [Testing].[Joins] ADD  DEFAULT ((1)) FOR [PrimaryGroup]
GO
```

**Add some data to table List e.g.**
```
Id	Description
18C2810D-58B9-EE11-B82E-000C296039A5	Test1
19C2810D-58B9-EE11-B82E-000C296039A5	Test2
